## 📈 Exploratory Data Analysis

The analysis includes:

- Data inspection
- Data type validation
- Missing value assessment
- Descriptive statistics
- Distribution analysis
- Marketing KPI evaluation
- Platform comparison
- Funnel analysis
- Campaign performance analysis
- Theme performance analysis
- Seasonal trend analysis
- Country-level performance analysis

---

## 📊 Key Marketing KPIs

The project evaluates marketing performance using:

- Revenue
- Advertising Spend
- Impressions
- Reach
- Clicks
- Conversions
- CPM (Cost per Mille)
- CTR (Click-Through Rate)
- CPC (Cost per Click)
- CPA (Cost per Acquisition)
- Conversion Rate
- ROAS (Return on Ad Spend)

---

## 📌 Key Insights

The analysis provides insights into:

- The highest-performing advertising platforms based on ROAS.
- Campaigns that generate the greatest revenue and conversions.
- Creative themes that consistently outperform others.
- Customer movement across the marketing funnel.
- Seasonal and holiday effects on campaign performance.
- Revenue contribution by country and market tier.
- The relationship between advertising spend and revenue.

